{"id": 782, "genre": 1001, "title": "你听过哪些你根本不懂的“你懂的”？", "description": "“你懂的”，一个藏污纳垢又暧昧不清的词语，包含的都是秘而不宣的苟且和自以为趣的无聊。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 3279, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183549ukc7ElOjCNKyUaQW.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-01-27T11:32:04Z", "options": [{"id": 50179, "content": "跟理发师说你懂得", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 421280}, {"id": 45061, "content": "领导说：方案再修改，我的意思你明白了吗，你听懂我的话了吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 110811}, {"id": 45063, "content": "对方说：我要修改成这样这样，我知道你们很辛苦，但是你懂的。?????", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 447154}, {"id": 44298, "content": "我其实并不是不喜欢你，只是。。。你懂的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 438, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2557}, {"id": 44299, "content": "甲方说，做成这样，这样，嗯，大气一点，高端一点，你懂的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 569, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 322013}, {"id": 44300, "content": "去哪里吃？\n你懂的！\n吃什么菜？\n你懂的！\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 196, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215261}, {"id": 44556, "content": "特殊服务。你懂的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 444191}, {"id": 44812, "content": "我又不是你，，懂什么鬼啊", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200915z3xSt5C2biRrDYHu.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 445376}, {"id": 44813, "content": "你懂的正确翻译：you should have known that.", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 357014}, {"id": 44303, "content": "额……你懂的", "image": null, "praise_count": 127, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241060}, {"id": 44309, "content": "过年，你懂的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281185}, {"id": 46869, "content": "呃…你懂吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456629}, {"id": 44310, "content": "很久没听到你懂的这个词了", "image": nul